title: Spoilers
content:
I know haw to beat the Utility room!
(dont continue if you want to figure it out on your own)





Go to the part on the ramp where there is a gap in the pipes above. Use the bug where keen climbs on a pole to get into a secret passage. Inside, go a little to the right, then up.
At the top, go to the right about 1 block from the edge, jump down. jump down again. now jump up so you grab onto the edge on the right. Climb up and you'll exit! [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-smile.gif[/img]

And Keenrush, the level in the demo (dont read on if you dont want it spoiled)...




...is the other secret level.
Now how to get there (again, dont read on)





Go to the section B of the ship, and where keens BWB was on section A, you'll find that it is a secret hidden level.[img]http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v609/genius314/picturekeen.bmp[/img]
